manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Discover Tampax Cardboard Applicator Tampons Stand out, be proud, and be you with Tampax Cardboard Tampons. With up to eight hours of comfortable protection, you can live without limits even during your regular flow days. Free of perfume, dyes, and chlorine bleaching, Tampax Cardboard Tampons are also clinically tested* to be gentle on skin, so you can feel confident about wearing them. *Clinical data on file

Tampax Cardboard Features & Benefits FormFit Protection FormFit design gently expands to fit your individual shape, so you can feel comfortable and confident during your period. Protective Skirt Featuring the anti-leak Protective Skirt, Tampax Cardboard Tampons offer backup protection to help stop leaks before they happen. Controlled Insertion The tampon’s cardboard applicator features an anti-slip grip that helps you hold the applicator and position the tampon in the right place for an easy and comfortable insertion.

FAQ How does TAMPAX help stop leaks? Tampax Cardboard Tampons are designed to expand widthwise to fit your individual form and have a LeakGuard skirt to help stop leaks before they happen. If I like TAMPAX, what other products would be right for me? For the ultimate in comfortable, dependable protection during your period, next time try Tampax Pearl, Tampax Pocket Pearl, and Tampax Pearl Active tampons.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cardboard is hard to come by
reviews.reviewText: If you use tampons, you know you stick with the brand and style that works. I have better success with the Tampax style than the ones shaped more like a cup. It's hard to find cardboard applicators now. I get that plastic glides more easily, but I have a heavy enough flow that it's just not an issue to use cardboard. Plus, cardboard breaks down and plastic doesn't. In a world with plastic straw bans, why not go after plastic applicators? Anyway, these are my go to, and not always in stores these days.
